snippet: Andy Murray survived a nervy fifth-set decider against Czech veteran Radek Stepanek to complete a 3-6 3-6 6-0 6-3 7-5 comeback win and scrape into the French Open second round on Tuesday....
lead_paragraph: Andy Murray survived a nervy fifth-set decider against Czech veteran Radek Stepanek to complete a 3-6 3-6 6-0 6-3 7-5 comeback win and scrape into the French Open second round on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Murray Battles Past Wily Stepanek in Cliffhanger
headline.main: Murray Battles Past Wily Stepanek in Cliffhanger
